<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>和平的；爱好和平的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Martin liked Gandhi’s ideas about <strong>peaceful protest</strong>.
马丁赞同甘地和平抗议的想法。</p><footer>北师大① – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>安静的；平静的：</strong></h4>
